NAME
    AnyEvent::Tickit - Use AnyEvent with Tickit user interface.

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
        use AnyEvent;
        use AnyEvent::Tickit;

        my $loop = AE::cv;

        my $tickit = AnyEvent::Tickit->new( cv => $cv );

        # Create some widgets
        # ...

        $tickit->set_root_widget( $rootwidget );

        # Create some AnyEvent event handlers
        # ...

        $tickit->run();

DESCRIPTION
    Use AnyEvent with Tickit user interface.

SEE ALSO
    *   Tickit::Async

